text: San Narciso (Spanish for "Saint Narcissus") is the name of two places in the Philippines: *San Narciso, Quezon *San Narciso, Zambales ;In other uses: * San Narciso, Belize * San Narciso, a fictional Californian city in Thomas Pynchon's The Crying of Lot 49 * 1867 San Narciso Hurricane, the costliest and deadliest storm of the 1867 Atlantic hurricane season
title: San Narciso
